t: Praise*p ye the Lord.*s Praise God in his sanctuary: praise him in the firmament of his power.
Praise*p him for his mighty acts: praise him according to his excellent greatness.
Praise*p him with the sound of the trumpet: praise him with the psaltery and harp.
Praise*p him with the timbrel and dance: praise him with stringed instruments and organs.
Praise*p him upon the loud cymbals: praise him upon the high sounding cymbals.
Let*p every thing that hath breath praise the Lord.*s Praise ye the Lord.*s
